text: Dmitry Matveyev (born 25 December 1984) is a Russian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Russia Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saint Petersburg
